ObjectStates.Name: Custom_Token
ObjectStates.LuaScript:
function onPickUp()
url = self.getCustomObject().image
version = url:gsub('{(.*)}', url)
local i = 1
local versions = {}
for version in string.gmatch(url, '{(.*)}') do
versions[i] = version
    i = i + 1
end

version = (versions[1])
version = (math.random(1,100000))
version = "{" .. version .. "}"

url = string.gsub(url, '{(.*)}', version)

self.setCustomObject({image = url})

end
